        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="install-certbot"><a href="#install-certbot" class="headerlink" title="install certbot"></a>install certbot</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">sudo snap install --classic certbot<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="准备certbot命令"><a href="#准备certbot命令" class="headerlink" title="准备certbot命令"></a>准备certbot命令</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">sudo ln -s &#x2F;snap&#x2F;bin&#x2F;certbot &#x2F;usr&#x2F;bin&#x2F;certbot<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="开始安装ssl"><a href="#开始安装ssl" class="headerlink" title="开始安装ssl"></a>开始安装ssl</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">sudo certbot --apache<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="测试自动更新"><a href="#测试自动更新" class="headerlink" title="测试自动更新"></a>测试自动更新</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">sudo certbot renew --dry-run<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="确认https能否访问"><a href="#确认https能否访问" class="headerlink" title="确认https能否访问"></a>确认https能否访问</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">访问https:&#x2F;&#x2F;your-ip.com&#x2F;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
      
